1
00:00:02,602 --> 00:00:05,003
<i>[ Broots ]</i>
<i>RAINES'S ESTRANGED WIFE ESCAPED</i>
<i>THAT MENTAL HOSPITAL...</i>

2
00:00:05,072 --> 00:00:07,038
<i>JUST TO TELL YOU ABOUT</i>
<i>YOUR MOTHER AND MIRAGE? WHY?</i>

3
00:00:07,107 --> 00:00:10,842
<i>[ Miss Parker ]</i>
<i>EDNA RAINES SAID MIRAGE</i>
<i>WAS MY MOTHER'S WORK.</i>

4
00:00:10,911 --> 00:00:12,844
WORK I'M SUPPOSED TO FINISH.

5
00:00:12,913 --> 00:00:16,949
WELL, NO ONE SEEMS TO REMEMBER
ANY CENTRE PROJECT BY THAT NAME.

6
00:00:17,017 --> 00:00:20,251
COULD IT BE
ONE OF HER DELUSIONS?
YOU DIDN'T SEE HER EYES.

7
00:00:20,320 --> 00:00:23,188
SYD, IN THAT MOMENT,
SHE WAS AS SANE AS YOU AND I.

8
00:00:25,158 --> 00:00:26,558
[ Scoffs ]

9
00:00:26,627 --> 00:00:29,260
<i>BROOTS, YOU BEEN</i>
<i>DOWNLOADING PORN AGAIN?</i>

10
00:00:29,329 --> 00:00:31,529
MY E-MAIL SERVER
IS WHACKED.

11
00:00:31,598 --> 00:00:36,735
[ Sighs ]
SOMEONE AROUND HERE<i> HAS</i> HEARD
OF MIRAGE. YOU CAN BET ON IT.

12
00:00:36,804 --> 00:00:40,705
EXCUSE ME, MA'AM.
I'M HERE TO COLLECT
BURN BAGS FOR INCINERATION.

13
00:00:47,847 --> 00:00:50,248
I... KNEW HER.

14
00:00:50,317 --> 00:00:52,717
EXCUSE ME?
CATHERINE.

15
00:00:56,022 --> 00:00:59,090
SHE WAS
A SPECIAL PERSON.
YOU KNEW MY MOTHER?

16
00:00:59,159 --> 00:01:03,261
AND SHE ALWAYS SEEMED LIKE
A BRIGHT AND SHINING SPIRIT...

17
00:01:03,330 --> 00:01:05,930
EVEN IN THE DARKEST HOURS.

18
00:01:09,169 --> 00:01:11,537
SORRY FOR THE INTERRUPTION.

19
00:01:16,009 --> 00:01:18,777
MAYBE WE COULD...
TALK AGAIN.

20
00:01:18,846 --> 00:01:21,446
IF YOU-- IF YOU
WOULDN'T MIND, MR., UM--

21
00:01:21,515 --> 00:01:24,449
NAME'S LEONARD.
AND IT WOULD BE MY PLEASURE.

22
00:01:51,178 --> 00:01:53,111
WHAT THE HELL
ARE YOU DOING?

23
00:01:53,180 --> 00:01:56,482
<i>EVERYTHING BURNS.</i>
MISS PARKER'LL WANT TO SEE THIS.

24
00:01:56,550 --> 00:01:58,349
I SAID EVERYTHING BURNS.

25
00:01:58,418 --> 00:02:00,585
MISS PARKER MUST SEE THIS.

26
00:02:00,654 --> 00:02:02,653
BIG MISTAKE, YOU DUMB--

27
00:02:02,722 --> 00:02:04,990
[ Grunts ]
<i> [ Gun Cocking ]</i>

28
00:02:05,059 --> 00:02:07,859
I HAVE TO TALK TO MISS PARKER.

29
00:02:10,664 --> 00:02:13,798
<i>[ Woman ]</i>
<i>DETAILS ARE SKETCHY, BUT AFTER</i>
<i>THE ROBBERY, THE FIVE SUSPECTS,</i>

30
00:02:13,867 --> 00:02:18,436
<i>POSING AS JANITORIAL STAFF,</i>
<i>FLED MAGNA TECHNOLOGIES</i>
<i>IN A BROWN VAN.</i>

31
00:02:18,505 --> 00:02:22,674
<i>A HAZMAT TEAM HAS BEEN</i>
<i>DISPATCHED, AND THE WAREHOUSE</i>
<i>DISTRICT HAS BEEN QUARANTINED.</i>

32
00:02:22,742 --> 00:02:25,977
<i>WE'LL KEEP YOU UPDATED</i>
<i>AS THE STORY UNFOLDS.</i>

33
00:02:26,046 --> 00:02:30,114
<i>REPORTING LIVE FROM</i>
<i>THE WAREHOUSE DISTRICT,</i>
<i>NOW BACK TO YOU IN THE STUDIO.</i>

34
00:02:32,119 --> 00:02:34,052
<i>[ Man Screaming ]</i>
<i>LET ME OUTTA HERE! LET ME OUT!</i>

35
00:02:34,121 --> 00:02:38,690
<i>[ People Coughing ]</i>

36
00:02:38,759 --> 00:02:41,292
MY THROAT IS ON FIRE.
I CAN'T BREATHE.

37
00:02:41,361 --> 00:02:43,628
<i>SOMETHING IS VERY WRONG HERE.</i>

38
00:02:45,265 --> 00:02:47,832
<i> OH, IT'S THIS.</i>
<i> IT'S WHAT WE STOLE.</i>

39
00:02:47,901 --> 00:02:52,304
[ Hissing ]
<i>[ Coughing Continues ]</i>

40
00:02:52,373 --> 00:02:55,139
OH, MY GOD.

41
00:02:55,208 --> 00:02:58,076
<i>HEY, SCIENCE GUY.</i>
<i>YOU'RE MAKING ME NERVOUS.</i>
<i>WHAT IS IT?</i>

42
00:02:58,145 --> 00:02:59,845
<i>[ Sirens Wail ]</i>
SOMAN NERVE GAS.

43
00:02:59,914 --> 00:03:01,913
- THAT STUFF COULD KILL US,
COULDN'T IT?
- IT ALREADY IS.

44
00:03:01,982 --> 00:03:05,717
- WHAT DO YOU MEAN, IS?
- IS. IS!

45
00:03:05,785 --> 00:03:10,489
BARRING SOME MIRACLE,
WE'RE ALL GOING TO BE DEAD
IN LESS THAN SIX HOURS.

46
00:03:15,929 --> 00:03:19,064
<i>[ Man Narrating ]</i>
<i>THERE ARE PRETENDERS AMONG US.</i>

47
00:03:19,133 --> 00:03:21,065
<i>[ Jarod ]</i>
<i>I WAS TAKEN FROM MY FAMILY.</i>

48
00:03:21,134 --> 00:03:24,703
<i>THIRTY-SIX HOURS AND HE'S</i>
<i>ALREADY DEMONSTRATING MORE</i>
<i>TALENT THAN ANY OF OUR OTHERS.</i>

49
00:03:24,771 --> 00:03:28,173
<i>HOW MANY PEOPLE DIED</i>
<i>BECAUSE OF WHAT I THOUGHT UP?</i>

50
00:03:28,242 --> 00:03:31,676
SINCE I BROKE OUT,
I'VE SPENT EVERY MOMENT
SEARCHING FOR MY PAST.

51
00:03:31,745 --> 00:03:33,945
<i>[ Miss Parker ]</i>
<i>HE'S A PRETENDER--</i>

52
00:03:34,014 --> 00:03:36,781
<i>A GENIUS WHO CAN BECOME</i>
<i>ANYONE THAT HE WANTS TO BE.</i>

53
00:03:36,850 --> 00:03:39,584
-<i> THE CENTRE WANTS HIM ALIVE.</i>
- PREFERABLY.

54
00:03:39,653 --> 00:03:42,587
<i>- [ Miss Parker ] HE DEFENDS</i>
<i>  THE WEAK AND ABUSED.</i>
<i>- [ Jarod ] LIFE'S A GIFT.</i>

55
00:03:54,367 --> 00:03:56,834
-<i> YOU A DOCTOR?</i>
- I AM TODAY.

56
00:04:02,209 --> 00:04:05,110
-<i> [ Broots ] MISS PARKER.</i>
- GOOD NIGHT, BROOTS.

57
00:04:05,179 --> 00:04:08,180
THAT GUY WENT POSTAL
DOWN IN SL 26.
STARTED SHOOTING UP THE PLACE.

58
00:04:08,248 --> 00:04:10,414
- THAT GUY?
- LEONARD, THE CLERK!

59
00:04:10,483 --> 00:04:12,850
<i> THE BURN BAG GUY</i>
<i> THAT KNEW YOUR MOTHER!</i>

60
00:04:20,560 --> 00:04:22,860
<i>[ Broots ]</i>
<i>GOD.</i>

61
00:04:24,565 --> 00:04:27,532
<i>WE TRIED TO</i>
<i>NEGOTIATE WITH HIM.</i>

62
00:04:30,704 --> 00:04:34,472
HE WASN'T INTERESTED.
SO YOU TRADED THE OLIVE
BRANCH FOR AN UZI.

63
00:04:34,541 --> 00:04:36,474
IS THAT YOUR CHRISTIAN WAY,
RAINES?

64
00:04:36,543 --> 00:04:39,510
HE WAS ARMED AND OUT OF CONTROL.
HE TRIED TO KILL ONE OF MY MEN.

65
00:04:39,579 --> 00:04:41,346
THERE MUST HAVE BEEN
ANOTHER WAY.

66
00:04:41,415 --> 00:04:45,049
I WILL NOT TOLERATE UNSTABLE
BEHAVIOR FROM CENTRE EMPLOYEES.

67
00:04:45,118 --> 00:04:47,786
I THOUGHT THAT WAS
A JOB REQUIREMENT.

68
00:04:52,692 --> 00:04:54,793
BROOTS.

69
00:04:57,798 --> 00:05:01,799
I WANT THE SURVEILLANCE
FOOTAGE OF WHAT JUST
HAPPENED HERE. QUICK.

70
00:05:01,868 --> 00:05:05,203
<i>[ Man ]</i>
<i>AIN'T BAD ENOUGH THERE'S COPS</i>
<i>SEARCHIN' FOR US EVERYWHERE.</i>

71
00:05:05,272 --> 00:05:07,972
<i>NOW YOU'RE TELLIN' US</i>
<i>WE GOT SIX HOURS TO LIVE?</i>

72
00:05:08,041 --> 00:05:11,175
WHO THE HELL ARE YOU TO BE
PRONOUNCING US DEAD ON ARRIVAL?

73
00:05:11,244 --> 00:05:15,013
I DON'T HAVE TO, MR. JOB.
YOU CAN ALREADY FEEL IT,
CAN'T YOU?

74
00:05:15,081 --> 00:05:17,382
YOU ALL CAN.
IT'S ON YOUR SKIN.

75
00:05:17,450 --> 00:05:20,685
<i>IT'S IN YOUR LUNGS.</i>
<i>AND IT ONLY GETS WORSE.</i>

76
00:05:20,754 --> 00:05:24,422
<i>[ Coughing ]</i>
<i> ELIJAH NEVER SAID ANYTHING</i>
<i> ABOUT STEALING NERVE GAS.</i>

77
00:05:24,490 --> 00:05:27,759
POINDEXTER HERE'S PROBABLY
TALKING OUT HIS ASS.

78
00:05:27,828 --> 00:05:32,029
I MEAN, US, WE KNOW
EACH OTHER, RIGHT? BUT HIM?
WHO THE HELL IS HE?

79
00:05:32,098 --> 00:05:36,367
<i>FOR ALL WE KNOW, HE'S SOME</i>
<i>OUT OF WORK PHARMACIST.</i>
<i>I THINK WE SHOULD CALL ELIJAH.</i>

80
00:05:36,436 --> 00:05:38,937
EVE'S RIGHT. WE WERE SUPPOSED TO
STEAL COMPUTER CHIPS.

81
00:05:39,005 --> 00:05:41,539
YEAH, NOT TO MENTION
100,000 EACH FOR OUR EFFORTS.

82
00:05:41,608 --> 00:05:44,276
<i> THANK YOU VERY MUCH.</i>
<i> I SAY WE CALL HIM.</i>

83
00:05:44,344 --> 00:05:47,679
ELIJAH SAID THE TARGET WAS
A BOX. THAT'S ALL HE SAID.

84
00:05:47,748 --> 00:05:51,382
WHAT DIFFERENCE DOES IT MAKE?
HE OWES US ANYWAY, RIGHT?

85
00:05:53,687 --> 00:05:56,287
SCREW IT.
I'M GONNA CALL ELIJAH.
NO. ELIJAH CALLS US!

86
00:05:56,356 --> 00:05:58,757
<i> ALWAYS HAS, HE ALWAYS WILL!</i>

87
00:05:58,826 --> 00:06:01,793
<i>[ Eve ] I DON'T KNOW ABOUT YOU,</i>
<i>BUT I'M NOT JUST GONNA SIT HERE</i>
<i>AND WAIT TO DIE.</i>

88
00:06:01,861 --> 00:06:05,930
<i>THERE MUST BE SOMETHING</i>
<i>WE CAN DO ABOUT THIS SOMAN GAS.</i>

89
00:06:05,999 --> 00:06:08,199
IT AFFECTS THE CHEMICAL
STRUCTURE OF THE BRAIN.

90
00:06:08,268 --> 00:06:12,437
<i>IT'S ONLY A MATTER OF TIME</i>
<i>BEFORE OUR PARANOIA</i>
<i>TURNS INTO PSYCHOSIS.</i>

91
00:06:12,506 --> 00:06:15,073
- WAIT. WHAT DO YOU MEAN?
WE ALL GO CRAZY?
- EXACTLY.

92
00:06:15,142 --> 00:06:19,144
<i>IT BREAKS DOWN OUR TISSUES.</i>
<i>FIRST WE'LL FEEL NAUSEOUS,</i>
<i>THEN THE TREMORS,</i>

93
00:06:19,212 --> 00:06:23,714
AND THEN, OUR INTERNAL ORGANS
WILL LIQUEFY.

94
00:06:23,783 --> 00:06:28,286
<i>OUR INSIDES WILL LOOK SOMETHING</i>
<i>LIKE, WELL, SOMETHING LIKE THAT.</i>

95
00:06:31,625 --> 00:06:33,959
THEN YOUR NOSE WILL START TO
BLEED, AND IT JUST WON'T--

96
00:06:34,027 --> 00:06:35,793
NO, STOP. OKAY? I JUST--
MAKE HIM STOP.

97
00:06:35,862 --> 00:06:39,163
<i>ALL RIGHT, I CAN'T--</i>
<i>[ Gags, Coughs ]</i>

98
00:06:39,232 --> 00:06:43,034
<i>LOOK. LOOK.</i>
<i>IT'S-IT'S ELIJAH'S LAPTOP.</i>

99
00:06:43,103 --> 00:06:45,269
HE'S GONNA HELP US.
<i>[ Eve ]</i>
<i>AND WHAT?</i>

100
00:06:45,338 --> 00:06:48,840
WE WAIT FOR HIS CALL AND-AND
THEN SURF THE WEB, MR. JOB?

101
00:06:48,908 --> 00:06:51,343
I HEAR BLEEDOUT.COM HAS
SOME REAL INTERESTING GRAPHICS.

102
00:06:51,411 --> 00:06:53,912
YOU'RE REALLY TURNING INTO
ONE SARCASTIC BITCH,
YOU KNOW THAT?

103
00:06:53,980 --> 00:06:56,982
OOH, YOU REALLY DO
HAVE ISSUES WITH WOMEN.

104
00:06:57,050 --> 00:06:59,084
WHAT WAS IT?
TRAUMA WITH TRAINING PANTS?

105
00:06:59,152 --> 00:07:01,652
OR DID MOMMY HAVE STOLI
WITH HER CORNFLAKES
EVERY MORNING?

106
00:07:01,721 --> 00:07:03,521
SHUT UP!
<i>OR WHAT?</i>

107
00:07:03,590 --> 00:07:06,958
YOU WANT TO SMACK ME AROUND
A LITTLE, HMM?
OKAY. THAT'S ENOUGH.

108
00:07:07,026 --> 00:07:10,628
<i>AS SICK AS WE'RE GOING TO GET,</i>
<i>WE NEED TO STICK TOGETHER.</i>

109
00:07:10,697 --> 00:07:13,631
<i>[ Hard Typing ]</i>
<i>THIS IS ELIJAH'S LAPTOP.</i>

110
00:07:13,700 --> 00:07:15,934
THE QUESTION IS WHY HASN'T
HE TRIED TO CONTACT US?

111
00:07:16,003 --> 00:07:18,836
HE USED US
AS GUINEA PIGS IS WHY.

112
00:07:18,905 --> 00:07:21,139
LOOK. ARE WE REALLY GONNA--
ARE WE GONNA DIE?

113
00:07:21,208 --> 00:07:23,874
NO, BROTHER.
WE'RE NOT GONNA DIE.
I PROMISE YOU THAT, OKAY?

114
00:07:23,943 --> 00:07:28,179
<i>I'M GONNA TAKE CARE OF YOU.</i>
<i>DON'T I ALWAYS TAKE CARE OF YOU?</i>
<i>I DON'T KNOW ABOUT YOU.</i>

115
00:07:28,248 --> 00:07:30,949
ME AND MY BROTHER, WE'RE GETTIN'
THE HELL OUT OF HERE.
COME ON. LET'S GO.

116
00:07:31,017 --> 00:07:34,185
- AND EXACTLY WHERE
DO YOU THINK YOU'RE GOING?
- TO A HOSPITAL.

117
00:07:34,254 --> 00:07:36,621
USE YOUR BRAINS, MR. CAIN.
WHAT'S LEFT OF THEM.

118
00:07:36,689 --> 00:07:39,323
<i>THE WAY THE BLACK-AND-WHITE'S</i>
<i>ARE CIRCLING AROUND OUTSIDE,</i>

119
00:07:39,392 --> 00:07:43,561
YOU AND YOUR BROTHER
WON'T GET A BLOCK
BEFORE THEY PICK YOU UP.

120
00:07:43,629 --> 00:07:49,333
ABRAHAM'S RIGHT. OUR BEST CHANCE
IS IF WE STICK TOGETHER AND
WAIT FOR ELIJAH TO CONTACT US.

121
00:07:53,106 --> 00:07:56,041
ALL RIGHT.

122
00:07:57,644 --> 00:08:00,311
<i>BUT IF THINGS GET OUT OF HAND,</i>

123
00:08:00,380 --> 00:08:03,982
THE LAST RATIONAL THOUGHT I'M
GONNA HAVE IS PUTTING A .38 SLUG
IN THE BACK OF YOUR HEAD.

124
00:08:04,050 --> 00:08:07,685
IF THIS GETS OUT OF HAND,
I WILL CONSIDER THAT A FAVOR.

125
00:08:07,754 --> 00:08:09,888
<i>[ Coughing ]</i>

126
00:08:13,860 --> 00:08:15,827
<i>[ Job ]</i>
<i>HEY, I'M GETTIN' SOMETHIN'.</i>

127
00:08:15,896 --> 00:08:19,530
<i>[ Woman ]</i>
<i>THE ROBBERY OCCURRED IN DALLAS'S</i>
<i>INDUSTRIAL DISTRICT.</i>

128
00:08:19,599 --> 00:08:22,367
NOW, FOR UNKNOWN REASONS,
THE AREA'S BEEN CORDONED OFF.

129
00:08:22,435 --> 00:08:25,269
AND AN EMERGENCY
EVACUATION ORDER HAS GONE OUT...

130
00:08:25,338 --> 00:08:28,539
TO CLEAR THE AREA
OF ALL NONEMERGENCY PERSONNEL.

131
00:08:28,608 --> 00:08:31,776
EVACUATION. COPS ALREADY
KNOW WHAT WE STOLE.

132
00:08:31,845 --> 00:08:35,379
IF THEY KNOW, THEN ELIJAH KNOWS.
YEAH, WELL, ELIJAH'S GONNA
WANT HIS STUFF, RIGHT?

133
00:08:35,448 --> 00:08:37,949
SO HE'S GONNA COME DOWN AND-AND
GET US OUT OF HERE, RIGHT?

134
00:08:38,018 --> 00:08:41,519
RIGHT. MAYBE HE'LL SEND A FLOCK
OF FLYING MONKEYS, MORON.

135
00:08:41,588 --> 00:08:44,522
HEY, LEAVE HIM ALONE. NOW.

136
00:08:44,591 --> 00:08:46,591
<i> [ Job ]</i>
<i> EASE UP, TARZAN.</i>

137
00:08:46,660 --> 00:08:48,760
YOU KNOW, I KNEW
I SHOULD HAVE CUT AND RUN...

138
00:08:48,828 --> 00:08:51,562
WHEN I REALIZED
YOU THOUGHT GROUNDHOG DAY
WAS A NATIONAL HOLIDAY.

139
00:08:52,933 --> 00:08:55,132
<i>I'M NOT SAYING</i>
<i>IT'S A MAJOR HOLIDAY.</i>

140
00:08:55,201 --> 00:08:57,969
<i>I'M JUST SAYING</i>
<i>IT'S RIGHT UP THERE</i>
<i>WITH, UH, SECRETARY'S DAY.</i>

141
00:08:58,038 --> 00:09:00,304
SECRETARY'S DAY ISN'T
A NATIONAL HOLIDAY EITHER, JOB.

142
00:09:00,373 --> 00:09:02,273
AND LIKE YOU'VE EVER
HAD A SECRETARY ANYWAY.

143
00:09:02,342 --> 00:09:04,408
I HAD A SECRETARY ONCE.

144
00:09:04,477 --> 00:09:08,646
AND THEN LUNCH WAS OVER,
WE PUT OUR CLOTHES BACK ON.
SHE WENT BACK TO HER TYPING.

145
00:09:08,715 --> 00:09:11,449
[ Laughs ]

146
00:09:15,855 --> 00:09:20,792
EH, SPEAKIN' OF SECRETARIES,
HOTSHOT, WHAT ARE YOU,
SOME KIND OF A ENTRY EXPERT?

147
00:09:20,861 --> 00:09:24,329
THE NAME MR. ELIJAH
GAVE ME IS MR. ABRAHAM.

148
00:09:24,397 --> 00:09:28,666
AND, YES, BREAKING AND ENTRY
IS ONE OF MY SPECIALTIES.

149
00:09:28,735 --> 00:09:32,003
I'LL BET YOU ROBBED A GIRL
OF HER VIRGINITY ONCE,
WHICH I FIND IMPRESSIVE.

150
00:09:32,072 --> 00:09:36,474
-<i> WELL, YOU SHOULD.</i>
<i> SHE WAS YOUR SISTER.</i>
- AHH! [ Laughing ]

151
00:09:36,543 --> 00:09:39,978
WHAT THE HELL ARE YOU
LAUGHIN' AT, HALF-WIT?
YOUR MAMA IS YOUR SISTER.

152
00:09:40,046 --> 00:09:43,848
- HEY.
- HOW DID YOU PEOPLE PULL OFF
20 SCORES IN THREE YEARS?

153
00:09:43,917 --> 00:09:46,851
I'LL TELL YOU HOW. WE DON'T KNOW
A DAMN THING ABOUT EACH OTHER.

154
00:09:46,919 --> 00:09:50,088
<i>RULE NUMBER ONE</i>
<i>IN THE BOOK OF MR. ELIJAH.</i>
<i> [ Electronic Ringing ]</i>

155
00:09:50,157 --> 00:09:54,425
[ Electronic Female Voice ]
YOU HAVE A VIDEO PHONE CALL.

156
00:09:54,494 --> 00:09:58,629
GOOD MORNING, CAMPERS.
I ASSUME YOU'VE ALL MET AND
BONDED WITH MR. ABRAHAM HERE.

157
00:09:58,698 --> 00:10:00,632
HE'S A STRONG ADDITION
TO OUR TEAM.

158
00:10:00,700 --> 00:10:03,368
HE'S AN EXPERT IN MANY AREAS,
MOSTLY THE SCIENCES.

159
00:10:03,437 --> 00:10:06,971
-WHAT? LIKE WE'RE MOPES
OR SOMETHING?
-GOOD TO SEE YOU AGAIN TOO, JOB.

160
00:10:07,040 --> 00:10:09,707
I GOTTA AGREE WITH JOB
ON THIS ONE. WE'VE DONE
FINE ON OUR OWN, MR. E.

161
00:10:09,776 --> 00:10:13,010
<i>HAVE WE?</i>
<i>I'M PUTTING MR. ABRAHAM</i>
<i>IN CHARGE OF THIS ONE.</i>

162
00:10:13,079 --> 00:10:16,847
WHAT?
I GOTTA TAKE ORDERS
FROM SCIENCE GUY HERE?

163
00:10:16,916 --> 00:10:20,117
<i>YOU KNOW, WE MADE</i>
<i>A LOT OF SCRATCH FOR YOU</i>
<i>IN THE PAST FEW YEARS, PAL.</i>

164
00:10:20,186 --> 00:10:22,519
I DON'T HAVE TO SIT HERE
AND TAKE THIS CRAP.

165
00:10:22,588 --> 00:10:25,623
WELL, THEN I GUESS
THE OTHERS WILL HAVE TO SPLIT UP
YOUR HUNDRED THOUSAND.

166
00:10:25,691 --> 00:10:28,993
WE GET A HUNDRED GRAND EACH?
<i>[ Elijah ]</i>
<i>IT'S BIG.</i>

167
00:10:29,062 --> 00:10:32,129
BUT LET'S SEE
IF WE CAN DO THIS ONE
WITHOUT ANY BLOOD ON IT. DEAL?

168
00:10:36,936 --> 00:10:39,971
<i>WHAT DEAL DOESN'T</i>
<i>HAVE BLOOD ON IT?</i>

169
00:10:40,040 --> 00:10:42,606
[ Coughing ]

170
00:11:00,760 --> 00:11:02,893
ISN'T THIS CUTE?

171
00:11:02,962 --> 00:11:04,962
<i>[ Jarod ]</i>
<i>WHAT IS IT?</i>

172
00:11:09,502 --> 00:11:13,103
BRITTANY TATE?
WHO'S BRITTANY TATE?

173
00:11:13,172 --> 00:11:17,709
LAST JOB WE DID,
THREE MONTHS AGO,
A KID WAS MURDERED.

174
00:11:17,777 --> 00:11:20,010
<i>[ Job Coughing ]</i>

175
00:11:24,150 --> 00:11:26,750
"BRITTANY TATE, AGE NINE,
WAS SMOTHERED TO DEATH...

176
00:11:26,819 --> 00:11:29,187
"DURING A ROBBERY
AT A WESTBROOK ESTATE.

177
00:11:30,923 --> 00:11:34,091
"ONLY EVIDENCE FOUND AT
THE SCENE WAS A PILLOW
USED IN THE SUFFOCATION,

178
00:11:34,160 --> 00:11:38,129
A SPILLED BOTTLE OF PERFUME
AND A BROKEN MUSIC BOX."

179
00:11:38,197 --> 00:11:41,566
WELL, I GUESS THAT'S WHAT
ELIJAH MEANT WHEN HE SAID,
"ONE WITHOUT BLOOD."

180
00:11:42,836 --> 00:11:44,769
WHICH ONE OF YOU GENIUSES
DID HER?

181
00:11:44,838 --> 00:11:46,904
<i>[ Job ]</i>
<i>NONE OF US KNOWS.</i>

182
00:11:46,973 --> 00:11:49,207
NOBODY'S TALKIN'.

183
00:11:52,545 --> 00:11:54,578
MR. CAIN'S
GONE STRANGELY SILENT.

184
00:11:56,382 --> 00:11:59,049
- SO?
- SO, YOU KILLED
THAT LITTLE GIRL.

185
00:11:59,118 --> 00:12:02,654
[ Chortles ]
LADY, YOUR BRAIN'S ALREADY
BEGINNING TO MELT.

186
00:12:03,990 --> 00:12:06,624
<i> WHAT DIFFERENCE</i>
<i> DOES IT MAKE WHO DID IT?</i>

187
00:12:06,692 --> 00:12:10,661
IT'S DONE.
<i> [ Electronic Ringing ]</i>

188
00:12:10,730 --> 00:12:13,263
<i>[ Eve Coughing ]</i>
<i>YOU HAVE A VIDEO PHONE CALL.</i>

189
00:12:13,332 --> 00:12:15,900
TOUGH EVENING, EH?
<i>[ Job ] TOUGH?</i>

190
00:12:15,969 --> 00:12:17,902
WE'VE ALL BEEN EXPOSED
TO NERVE GAS!

191
00:12:17,971 --> 00:12:20,939
WHICH MEANS YOU'VE ACCOMPLISHED
YOUR MISSION. WELL DONE.

192
00:12:21,007 --> 00:12:24,608
YOU SET US UP?
YOU KNEW WHAT WE
WERE STEALING WAS DEADLY!

193
00:12:24,677 --> 00:12:26,644
WOULD YOU HAVE TAKEN
THE ASSIGNMENT OTHERWISE?

194
00:12:26,712 --> 00:12:28,913
ASSIGNMENT?
WE'RE DYING IN HERE!

195
00:12:28,982 --> 00:12:31,850
ONE OF THE CANISTERS LEAKED.
WE'VE ALL BEEN EXPOSED
TO THE GAS.

196
00:12:31,918 --> 00:12:35,653
<i>I REALIZED THAT THAT</i>
<i>MIGHT BE A POSSIBILITY.</i>
<i>CHECK THE DISPATCHER'S OFFICE.</i>

197
00:12:35,721 --> 00:12:38,489
I'VE LEFT MATERIALS THERE
FOR YOU TO WORK
A LITTLE CHEMISTRY, ABRAHAM.

198
00:12:38,558 --> 00:12:41,826
<i>NOW, I'M SENDING</i>
<i>A COUPLE OF MY MEN OVER</i>
<i>TO PICK UP THE CANISTERS.</i>

199
00:12:41,894 --> 00:12:44,262
THEY SHOULD BE AT YOUR LOCATION
WITHIN THE NEXT FEW HOURS.

200
00:12:44,330 --> 00:12:47,498
AND JUST KNOW THE CONTINGENCY
PLANS ARE BEING IMPLEMENTED.

201
00:12:47,567 --> 00:12:50,134
FORGET ABOUT CONTINGENCY.
WHAT ABOUT CURRENCY?

202
00:12:50,203 --> 00:12:52,704
PATIENCE, JOB. PATIENCE.

203
00:12:52,772 --> 00:12:54,706
MY MEN ARE ON THE WAY.
<i>[ Job ] NO, NO, WAIT.</i>

204
00:12:54,774 --> 00:12:58,409
WAIT. DAMN IT!

205
00:12:58,478 --> 00:13:00,845
OH, GOD.
HE'S-HE'S LEAVIN' US
HERE TO DIE.

206
00:13:00,914 --> 00:13:02,947
SHUT HIM UP, OR I WILL.

207
00:13:03,015 --> 00:13:04,949
[ Coughing ]

208
00:13:05,018 --> 00:13:07,218
ELIJAH WILL NOT LEAVE US
HIGH AND DRY, OKAY?

209
00:13:09,289 --> 00:13:11,623
WHAT'S THIS STUFF?

210
00:13:11,691 --> 00:13:14,324
ELIJAH LEFT ME EVERYTHING
I MIGHT NEED TO
CREATE AN ANTIDOTE.

211
00:13:14,393 --> 00:13:18,062
- YOU THINK YOU CAN SAVE US?
- NOW DON'T YOU WISH
YOU'D BEEN NICER TO ME?

212
00:13:21,467 --> 00:13:25,770
HEY, HOW LONG?
FIVE HOURS. MAYBE LESS.

213
00:13:25,839 --> 00:13:28,005
HOW-HOW DO WE KNOW
THAT YOU CAN DO THIS?

214
00:13:28,074 --> 00:13:32,042
I WAS AN ARMY MEDIC IN
DESERT STORM. I KNOW A FEW
THINGS ABOUT CHEMICAL WEAPONS.

215
00:13:36,549 --> 00:13:38,316
HEY, SCREW THIS.

216
00:13:39,552 --> 00:13:41,819
<i>THIS GUY COULD BE A WACKO</i>
<i>FOR ALL WE KNOW.</i>

217
00:13:41,888 --> 00:13:44,321
I AGREE WITH CAIN.
I'M GONNA TAKE MY CHANCES
WITH THE HOSPITAL.

218
00:13:44,391 --> 00:13:48,826
<i>YOU WON'T MAKE IT.</i>
<i>AND EVEN IF YOU DID, THEY WON'T</i>
<i>HAVE THE ANTIDOTE YOU NEED.</i>

219
00:13:48,895 --> 00:13:51,729
YOU'VE GOT ALL THE ANSWERS,
DON'T YOU?

220
00:13:52,965 --> 00:13:54,899
I'M OUTTA HERE.

221
00:13:54,967 --> 00:13:56,934
<i>[ Metal Clicks ]</i>
SOMEONE'S COMING.

222
00:13:58,671 --> 00:14:01,572
[ Job ]
COPS.

223
00:14:05,078 --> 00:14:09,013
[ Radio Chatter ]

224
00:14:17,090 --> 00:14:20,090
HEY, COME ON.
IT'S EMPTY. LET'S KEEP MOVING.

225
00:14:21,894 --> 00:14:24,629
<i>[ Man On Radio ]</i>
<i>THIRTEEN, SERGEANT,</i>
<i>ONE AND CENTRAL.</i>

226
00:14:26,633 --> 00:14:30,101
-<i> [ Door Closes ]</i>
- THEY'RE GONE. WE'RE CLEAR.

227
00:14:30,170 --> 00:14:33,137
<i>[ Light Coughing ]</i>

228
00:14:36,109 --> 00:14:38,709
<i>WE HAVE TO DO THIS</i>
<i>BEFORE IT'S TOO LATE.</i>

229
00:14:55,895 --> 00:14:58,730
[ No Audio ]

230
00:15:00,966 --> 00:15:04,635
- LEONARD DIDN'T KILL ANYONE.
- GOD, THEY JUST
MOWED THEM DOWN.

231
00:15:04,704 --> 00:15:06,671
REWIND, BROOTS.

232
00:15:06,739 --> 00:15:08,673
BEFORE THEY GET SHOT.

233
00:15:14,314 --> 00:15:16,246
<i>WHO'S HE CALLING?</i>

234
00:15:16,315 --> 00:15:18,182
CAN'T TELL.
THE IMAGE IS TOO SMALL.

235
00:15:18,250 --> 00:15:21,652
MAYBE IF I ENHANCE THE VIDEO,
ISOLATE HIS HANDS
AND MATCH THE MOTION.

236
00:15:21,721 --> 00:15:24,088
YOU CAN DO THAT?
WELL, YEAH.
IT WOULD TAKE ABOUT AN HOUR.

237
00:15:24,156 --> 00:15:27,358
[ Sighs ]
CLOCK'S TICKING.

238
00:15:28,561 --> 00:15:34,532
♪♪ [ Piano ]

239
00:15:38,671 --> 00:15:41,906
<i>[ Abel ]</i>
<i>SONG REMINDS ME</i>
<i>OF WHEN MOM USED TO SING IT.</i>

240
00:15:41,975 --> 00:15:46,410
<i> [ Eve Coughs ]</i>
<i>♪♪ [ Resumes ]</i>

241
00:15:48,548 --> 00:15:51,382
[ Static Hissing ]

242
00:15:57,123 --> 00:15:59,257
SIGNAL'S COMIN' BACK.

243
00:15:59,325 --> 00:16:02,993
THE LATEST REPORT IS THAT
THE SECURITY GUARD,
A FATHER OF SIX,

244
00:16:03,062 --> 00:16:07,331
WAS FOUND NEARLY STRANGLED
TO DEATH IN THE ROBBERY AT
MAGNA TECHNOLOGIES, LIMITED.

245
00:16:07,400 --> 00:16:10,534
HIS CONDITION
IS CONSIDERED TO BE
LIFE-THREATENING.

246
00:16:10,603 --> 00:16:13,070
POLICE ARE STILL COMBING
THE AREA FOR THE SUSPECTS.

247
00:16:13,139 --> 00:16:15,039
WHO DID IT?

248
00:16:16,442 --> 00:16:18,375
<i>WHICH ONE OF YOU IDIOTS</i>
<i>STRANGLED THE GUARD?</i>

249
00:16:18,445 --> 00:16:23,413
-WHAT DIFFERENCE DOES IT MAKE?
-IT MIGHT MAKE A BIG DIFFERENCE,
IF WE SURVIVE.

250
00:16:23,482 --> 00:16:26,750
THE QUESTION IS,
WHICH ONE OF YOU
HAS THE ITCHY TRIGGER FINGER?

251
00:16:32,425 --> 00:16:35,492
<i>♪♪ [ Piano Continues ]</i>

252
00:16:35,561 --> 00:16:40,131
[ Coughing ]

253
00:16:42,101 --> 00:16:45,436
TELL ME SOMETHING. WHAT DOES
ELIJAH SEE IN THAT ONE?

254
00:16:46,840 --> 00:16:50,407
IT'S LIKE A HORSE RACE ENTRY.
YOU WANT CAIN, YOU GET ABEL.

255
00:16:50,476 --> 00:16:53,610
[ Coughing Hard ]

256
00:16:55,481 --> 00:16:57,448
I GOTTA GET OUTTA HERE.
I GOTTA GET OUT. I GOTTA--

257
00:16:57,516 --> 00:16:59,449
<i> HEY, CALM DOWN.</i>
NO, I GOTTA GET OUTTA HERE.

258
00:16:59,518 --> 00:17:01,852
CALM DOWN.
CALM DOWN. CALM DOWN.
PLEASE!

259
00:17:01,921 --> 00:17:05,256
YOU KNOW SOMETHING? I THOUGHT
I WAS A REALLY GOOD JUDGE
OF PEOPLE. GUESS I WAS WRONG.

260
00:17:05,324 --> 00:17:07,258
<i> WHAT'S THAT</i>
<i> SUPPOSED TO MEAN?</i>

261
00:17:07,326 --> 00:17:09,960
THOUGHT I WAS WORKING
WITH PROFESSIONALS.
YOU SNUFF OUT A LITTLE GIRL.

262
00:17:10,029 --> 00:17:12,462
NOW A RENT-A-COP.
DID YOU DO IT?

263
00:17:12,531 --> 00:17:15,166
WHAT ABOUT YOU, MR. JOB?
[ Laughs ]

264
00:17:15,234 --> 00:17:17,534
YEAH, HE'S GOT THE GUTS.

265
00:17:17,603 --> 00:17:21,338
OH, YEAH.
KILLIN' A LITTLE GIRL,
THAT TAKES A LOT OF GUTS.

266
00:17:21,407 --> 00:17:23,874
FACE IT, YOU KNOW.
IT COULD'VE BEEN
ANY ONE OF US.

267
00:17:23,943 --> 00:17:26,144
SPEAK FOR YOURSELF.
LOOK, IT WASN'T ME.

268
00:17:26,212 --> 00:17:29,480
WELL, ONE GUILTY,
ALL GUILTY.
I'LL TELL YOU ONE THING.

269
00:17:29,549 --> 00:17:34,484
MR. SPARKY AND HIS
2,200 BOLTS OF DEATH,
HE DOESN'T MUCH CARE.

270
00:17:34,553 --> 00:17:36,486
WHAT ABOUT YOU, HUH?
YEAH?

271
00:17:36,556 --> 00:17:39,056
YOU COULD'VE POPPED THAT GUARD
JUST AS EASY AS ANY ONE OF US.

272
00:17:39,124 --> 00:17:43,895
YEAH. WE ALL KNOW EACH OTHER.
WE'VE BEEN DOING THIS A WHILE.
YOU? WE DON'T EVEN KNOW YOU.

273
00:17:43,963 --> 00:17:46,096
NO. YOU DON'T.

274
00:17:46,165 --> 00:17:49,866
<i>JOB WILL ACCESS</i>
<i>THE MAIN SECURITY PANEL AND</i>
<i>BREAK THE VARIOUS DOOR CODES,</i>

275
00:17:49,935 --> 00:17:52,502
AND CONTROL PANELS
TO THE SECURITY CAMERAS.

276
00:17:52,571 --> 00:17:54,672
EVE, CAIN AND I WILL TAKE
THE UPPER FLOOR,

277
00:17:54,741 --> 00:17:58,509
WITH EVE MANNING
THE INFRARED THERMAL SENSOR,
AND ME SECURING THE TARGET.

278
00:17:58,578 --> 00:18:00,511
YOU SURE THE TARGET'S
ON THE UPPER FLOOR?

279
00:18:00,580 --> 00:18:03,780
<i>IT'S SUPPOSED TO BE.</i>
<i>WHAT I DO KNOW IS THAT</i>
<i>IT'S KEPT IN COLD STORAGE.</i>

280
00:18:03,849 --> 00:18:06,617
THAT'S WHERE THE INFRARED
THERMAL GRID COMES IN.

281
00:18:06,686 --> 00:18:10,721
- WHAT ABOUT HIM?
- WE WALK IN PAST
THE SECURITY GUARD.

282
00:18:10,789 --> 00:18:12,723
THE JANITOR UNIFORMS
ARE ALREADY SET.

283
00:18:12,792 --> 00:18:15,426
[ Chuckles ]
JANITOR?

284
00:18:15,495 --> 00:18:19,262
HEY, A GUY LIKE ME IS
GONNA BE HARD-PRESSED
TO PASS FOR A BUCKET JOCKEY.

285
00:18:19,331 --> 00:18:22,533
YOU HAVE A BETTER IDEA,
MR. JOB?
YEAH. I DO.

286
00:18:22,602 --> 00:18:25,436
I, FOR ONE, WANT TO KNOW
WHO THE HELL YOU ARE,
MR. PEABODY.

287
00:18:25,504 --> 00:18:30,641
YOU KNOW ELIJAH'S RULE.
TOTAL ANONYMITY. NO NAMES,
NO PASTS, NOTHING.

288
00:18:30,710 --> 00:18:33,644
- I ALREADY BROKE THAT RULE.
- WHAT? WHAT ARE YOU
TALKIN' ABOUT?

289
00:18:33,713 --> 00:18:37,982
I SWIPED YOUR GLASS FROM
THE COFFEE SHOP LAST WEEK. I HAD
A FRIEND OF MINE RUN THE PRINTS.

290
00:18:38,050 --> 00:18:41,418
THERE AIN'T SQUAT
ON YOU OUT THERE.
YOU KNOW WHAT I'M SAYIN'?

291
00:18:41,487 --> 00:18:45,322
I MEAN, HELL, EVERY DECENT
CRIMINAL I KNOW HAS GOT
SOME KIND OF SHEET.

292
00:18:45,391 --> 00:18:48,059
WHAT'S THE MATTER?
YOU NEVER
BROKE THE LAW BEFORE?

293
00:18:48,127 --> 00:18:50,294
I BROKE PLENTY.

294
00:18:50,363 --> 00:18:52,296
I AM JUST TOO DAMN SMART,
TOO DAMN GOOD...

295
00:18:52,365 --> 00:18:54,998
AND LIKE MY FREEDOM
TOO DAMN MUCH
TO EVER GET CAUGHT.

296
00:18:55,067 --> 00:18:58,769
BUT, YOU, MR. JOB,
ON THE OTHER HAND--
[ Chuckles ]

297
00:19:00,339 --> 00:19:02,272
WHAT'S SO FUNNY?

298
00:19:02,342 --> 00:19:05,475
WELL, LET'S JUST SAY THAT
I RAN A LITTLE FINGERPRINT CHECK
ON YOU AS WELL.

299
00:19:05,544 --> 00:19:11,215
DO YOU MIND TELLING ME
EXACTLY WHAT DETERMINES
A LEWD ACT... AT A KENNEL?

300
00:19:19,825 --> 00:19:23,760
[ Coughing ]

301
00:19:23,829 --> 00:19:26,463
HEY, SIMPLE SIMON,<i> FINI.</i>

302
00:19:28,134 --> 00:19:33,137
WHY IS, UH, THIS GUY SO MUCH
WORSE THAN THE REST OF US?

303
00:19:34,574 --> 00:19:37,307
EACH ONE OF US IS DIFFERENT.
[ Sighs ]

304
00:19:38,444 --> 00:19:41,111
WE'LL ALL UNRAVEL
AT OUR OWN GENETIC PACE.

305
00:19:41,180 --> 00:19:45,382
OH. WELL, HE'S DEFINITELY
BRINGING UP THE REAR.

306
00:19:49,888 --> 00:19:53,390
LADIES AND GENTLEMEN, MR. ABEL
AND HIS FIVE-PIECE CONCERTO.

307
00:19:53,458 --> 00:19:57,061
<i>WELL, SIX,</i>
<i>IF YOU COUNT THE GREEN BEAN.</i>
<i>[ Grunts ]</i>

308
00:19:57,129 --> 00:19:58,795
LEAVE HIM ALONE.

309
00:20:00,967 --> 00:20:04,101
[ Coughing ]
I'M SO SORRY. MAMA'S
GONNA BE SO MAD AT ME.

310
00:20:04,170 --> 00:20:06,136
COME ON!
I GOTTA CLEAN THIS UP.

311
00:20:06,205 --> 00:20:08,539
<i> - DON'T DO THAT!</i>
<i> - I GOTTA CLEAN THIS UP.</i>

312
00:20:08,608 --> 00:20:12,509
COME ON. GET OUTTA THERE.
MOM'S DEAD!

313
00:20:12,578 --> 00:20:14,579
YOU IDIOT! YOU STUPID IDIOT!

314
00:20:14,647 --> 00:20:18,482
SHE'S DEAD!
HAS BEEN FOR 10 YEARS!
WAKE UP!

315
00:20:24,924 --> 00:20:29,092
I'M GONNA KILL THE NEXT PERSON
WHO SAYS A WORD.

316
00:20:47,013 --> 00:20:48,945
HOW'S IT COMING ALREADY, HUH?

317
00:20:49,014 --> 00:20:52,850
- I'M WORKIN' ON IT.
- YEAH? WELL, HURRY.

318
00:20:52,918 --> 00:20:56,687
YOU SHOULD SIT DOWN. IT WILL
SLOW THE EFFECTS OF THE TOXIN.

319
00:20:56,756 --> 00:20:59,723
[ Coughing, Gasping ]

320
00:21:04,497 --> 00:21:08,933
LOOK, I, UH--

321
00:21:09,001 --> 00:21:13,904
I DIDN'T
GIVE YOU MY BLOOD BEFORE
BECAUSE I WAS WORRIED.

322
00:21:13,973 --> 00:21:16,073
ABOUT WHAT?

323
00:21:18,111 --> 00:21:21,212
I'M PREGNANT.

324
00:21:21,280 --> 00:21:24,081
FOUR MONTHS.

325
00:21:25,752 --> 00:21:28,285
DO THEY KNOW?

326
00:21:28,353 --> 00:21:31,221
YEAH, SURE.

327
00:21:31,290 --> 00:21:34,892
THEY'D GIVE ME
A PERFECT LITTLE BABY SHOWER,
DON'T YOU THINK?

328
00:21:40,232 --> 00:21:42,299
SO WHAT'S THIS GAS
GONNA DO TO MY BABY?

329
00:21:42,367 --> 00:21:45,669
AIRBORNES-- THEY CAN'T PASS
THROUGH A PLACENTA.

330
00:21:45,738 --> 00:21:49,172
<i>ACTUALLY, YOUR BABY'S</i>
<i>SAFER THAN YOU ARE.</i>

331
00:21:50,642 --> 00:21:54,345
<i> OKAY.</i>
<i> Y-YOU CAN TAKE MY BLOOD.</i>

332
00:21:54,414 --> 00:21:56,647
AS-AS LONG AS IT'S SAFE
FOR THE BABY.

333
00:21:56,716 --> 00:21:58,648
I PROMISE.

334
00:22:00,853 --> 00:22:04,021
GOT IT?
GOT IT.

335
00:22:04,089 --> 00:22:08,926
<i>BUT YOU'RE NOT GONNA LIKE IT.</i>
<i>HE'S DIALING 2725.</i>

336
00:22:08,994 --> 00:22:10,928
<i>[ Miss Parker ]</i>
<i>MY EXTENSION.</i>

337
00:22:10,996 --> 00:22:13,197
MY GOD.

338
00:22:15,535 --> 00:22:18,702
[ Beeps, Rewinds ]

339
00:22:18,770 --> 00:22:22,206
<i>MISS PARKER, THIS IS LEONARD.</i>
<i>I SAW SOMETHING I PROBABLY</i>
<i>SHOULDN'T HAVE.</i>

340
00:22:22,274 --> 00:22:25,175
<i>SOMETHING MEANT TO BE</i>
<i>BURNED. MEMO B437.</i>

341
00:22:25,244 --> 00:22:28,212
<i>IT'S SOMETHING ABOUT</i>
<i>AN E-MAIL FILE INTERCEPTED</i>
<i>FROM YOUR COMPUTER.</i>

342
00:22:28,280 --> 00:22:30,347
<i>MISS PARKER,</i>
<i>YOU SHOULD SEE THIS.</i>

343
00:22:30,416 --> 00:22:32,849
<i>[ Gunfire ]</i>
<i>[ Leonard Grunts ]</i>

344
00:22:35,888 --> 00:22:38,555
SOMEONE BROKE
INTO YOUR COMPUTER. THAT'S WHY
YOUR E-MAIL WASN'T WORKING.

345
00:22:38,624 --> 00:22:40,557
DOESN'T THE CENTRE'S
SYSTEM KEEP, UH,

346
00:22:40,626 --> 00:22:43,027
DUPLICATES OF-OF
ALL INCOMING
AND OUTGOING E-MAILS?

347
00:22:43,096 --> 00:22:45,729
YEAH, IN THE FILE
ALLOCATION DUMP. NONE OF US
HAVE CLEARANCE THERE.

348
00:22:45,798 --> 00:22:49,333
GET ME THAT E-MAIL, BROOTS.
OR SOMEONE MIGHT FIND
ALL OF US IN THE DUMP.

349
00:22:51,437 --> 00:22:54,004
<i>NOW I'M GONNA DIE</i>
<i>'CAUSE OF MARK BEYER'S BIKE.</i>

350
00:22:54,073 --> 00:22:56,006
COME AGAIN.

351
00:22:56,075 --> 00:22:57,641
FIRST THING I EVER STOLE.

352
00:22:59,277 --> 00:23:01,645
YOU KNOW, IT HAD
THIS SPEED SHIFTER
AND THIS BANANA SEAT.

353
00:23:01,713 --> 00:23:04,582
<i>IT WAS THE MOST BEAUTIFUL THING</i>
<i>I EVER SAW.</i>

354
00:23:04,650 --> 00:23:09,920
IT WAS ALMOST WORTH THE COPS
CHASING ME JUST SO I COULD RIDE
THAT THING DOWN ARLINGTON HILL.

355
00:23:09,989 --> 00:23:12,689
WHERE DID ELIJAH
RECRUIT THESE TWO?
THE BOY SCOUTS?

356
00:23:15,093 --> 00:23:17,728
HEY, LOOK AT THIS.

357
00:23:20,165 --> 00:23:23,433
THAT BRITTANY GIRL,
HER BODY...

358
00:23:23,502 --> 00:23:26,836
WAS FOUND STUFFED IN A TOY CHEST
JUST LIKE THIS, WASN'T IT?

359
00:23:26,906 --> 00:23:28,571
WHAT THE HELL
IS GOING ON?

360
00:23:28,640 --> 00:23:33,410
I MEAN, THE PAPER IS ONE THING,
BUT THIS? THIS IS ELIJAH!

361
00:23:33,479 --> 00:23:36,746
- HE'S MESSING WITH OUR MINDS!
- WHAT DIFFERENCE DOES IT MAKE?

362
00:23:38,684 --> 00:23:41,885
WE NEED TO KEEP OUR MINDS IN
THE HERE AND THE NOW. WHO CARES
WHAT HAPPENED MONTHS AGO?

363
00:23:41,954 --> 00:23:45,188
I AGREE! THE HERE AND NOW!

364
00:23:45,257 --> 00:23:48,925
LIKE-LIKE HOW I
WANT MY HUNDRED GRAND.
HERE AND NOW.

365
00:23:48,994 --> 00:23:51,795
WHERE'S THE PAY? HUH?
WHERE?

366
00:23:51,864 --> 00:23:55,098
WE DID THE JOB!
WE DID THE DAMN JOB!

367
00:24:24,330 --> 00:24:26,596
[ Beeping ]

368
00:24:40,045 --> 00:24:43,680
- [ Beeps ]
- THERE WE GO, BOYS AND GIRLS.

369
00:24:43,749 --> 00:24:47,084
READY TO LOOP SIGNAL
ON SECURITY CAMERA ONE.
[ Beeps ]

370
00:24:51,824 --> 00:24:53,757
CLEAR.
GO.

371
00:24:53,826 --> 00:24:57,961
SECURITY DOOR CODE
IS 88656.

372
00:24:58,030 --> 00:24:59,963
[ Beeping ]

373
00:25:05,204 --> 00:25:08,471
<i>YOU'RE CLEAR.</i>

374
00:25:16,448 --> 00:25:18,682
<i>[ Eve ]</i>
<i>I HAVE INFRARED READINGS.</i>

375
00:25:18,751 --> 00:25:22,486
I'M GETTING EXTREME
TEMPERATURE DROP IN ROOM 2108.
THAT ONE.

376
00:25:22,555 --> 00:25:25,855
SECURITY CAMERA--

377
00:25:28,027 --> 00:25:33,530
CLEAR. SECURITY DOOR CODE
IS 61684.

378
00:25:50,683 --> 00:25:52,749
<i>YOU'RE IN THE CLEAN ROOM.</i>

379
00:26:00,092 --> 00:26:03,526
THE COLD ROOM
CHAMBER DOOR CODE IS...

380
00:26:03,595 --> 00:26:08,866
202018.

381
00:26:08,934 --> 00:26:13,136
[ Beeping ]

382
00:26:16,174 --> 00:26:18,442
[ Bang ]

383
00:26:18,510 --> 00:26:22,212
- NEXT TIME, KNOCK.
- YOUR LIMO AWAITS.

384
00:26:27,352 --> 00:26:31,555
<i> JOB, ARE WE CLEAR?</i>
<i> JOB, ARE WE CLEAR</i>
<i> TO COME OUT? JOB?</i>

385
00:26:31,624 --> 00:26:35,092
- [ Jarod ] COME ON.
- WAIT. JOB, ARE WE CLEAR?

386
00:26:35,160 --> 00:26:36,760
THE HELL WITH IT! COME ON!

387
00:26:39,464 --> 00:26:41,398
THERE'S NO GUARD.
WHERE'S THE GUARD?

388
00:26:41,466 --> 00:26:43,500
MY COMMUNICATION PIECES
SHORTED OUT. SORRY.

389
00:26:43,569 --> 00:26:46,369
DON'T YOU EVER LEAVE ME
HANGING OUT LIKE THAT AGAIN.
YOU UNDERSTAND?

390
00:26:46,438 --> 00:26:49,306
-<i> [ Alarm Beeping ]</i>
- COME ON, MOVE!
LET'S GET OUTTA HERE! MOVE!

391
00:26:49,375 --> 00:26:52,943
<i>[ Eve Coughing ]</i>

392
00:26:53,012 --> 00:26:57,514
<i> [ Groans ]</i>
<i> MY INSIDES</i>
<i> ARE STARTING TO BOIL.</i>

393
00:26:57,583 --> 00:26:59,683
COME ON.
IT WON'T BE LONG NOW.
[ Groaning ]

394
00:26:59,752 --> 00:27:01,685
I DON'T WANT TO
LOSE MY BABY.

395
00:27:01,754 --> 00:27:06,824
YOU WON'T.
NOT-NOT IF I CAN HELP IT.
[ Crying ]

396
00:27:06,892 --> 00:27:12,329
THANK YOU. THERE'S NOT A LOT OF
LOVE IN THIS ROOM, YOU KNOW?

397
00:27:12,397 --> 00:27:14,831
<i>[ Coughing ]</i>

398
00:27:19,071 --> 00:27:23,740
<i>♪♪ [ Music Box ]</i>

399
00:27:28,313 --> 00:27:31,348
OH, MY--
IT'S HER STUFF.

400
00:27:33,151 --> 00:27:34,851
<i>- [ Job ] WHOSE STUFF?</i>
-<i> [ Abel ] BRITTANY TATE.</i>

401
00:27:34,920 --> 00:27:36,853
THE DEAD GIRL'S STUFF.
IT'S HER STUFF.
WHAT?

402
00:27:36,922 --> 00:27:39,188
HER STUFF.
WHAT ARE YOU BABBLIN' ABOUT?

403
00:27:41,192 --> 00:27:44,161
NOTHIN' IN THERE.

404
00:27:44,230 --> 00:27:46,563
<i> NO. NO.</i>

405
00:27:46,631 --> 00:27:51,768
NO. I SAW A DOLL, AND A PILLOW,
A PICTURE, A MUSIC BOX.

406
00:27:51,837 --> 00:27:53,804
LISTEN, I SMELLED PERFUME.
[ Coughs ]

407
00:27:53,873 --> 00:27:56,907
<i> THE GUY'S STARTIN'</i>
<i> TO LOSE IT HERE.</i>

408
00:27:56,975 --> 00:27:59,676
I DON'T WANT TO DIE. I DON'T
WANT TO DIE. NOT LIKE THIS.
[ Gasping ]

409
00:27:59,745 --> 00:28:02,212
<i>[ Eve ]</i>
<i>OH, MY SKIN'S ON FIRE.</i>

410
00:28:02,281 --> 00:28:04,614
COME ON, SCIENCE GUY.
WHAT'S TAKIN' SO LONG?

411
00:28:05,951 --> 00:28:08,719
FREEZE!

412
00:28:17,797 --> 00:28:21,165
ELIJAH'S NOT GONNA LIKE IT
IF YOU EXECUTE HIS MESSENGERS.

413
00:28:21,233 --> 00:28:23,366
- ELIJAH?
- SENT US TO PICK UP THE GAS.

414
00:28:23,435 --> 00:28:25,836
[ Cain ] DIRTY COPS
AS MESSENGER BOYS?
TYPICAL ELIJAH.

415
00:28:25,905 --> 00:28:28,872
<i> HEY, MAN,</i>
<i> YOU GOT OUR MONEY?</i>

416
00:28:37,583 --> 00:28:40,250
- WHAT IS THIS? A JOKE?
- WHAT? WHAT IS IT?

417
00:28:40,319 --> 00:28:44,521
THERE'S LIKE 10 GRAND HERE.
HEY, THE DEAL WAS
ONE HUNDRED GRAND EACH.

418
00:28:44,590 --> 00:28:47,424
MR. ELIJAH IS
LESS THAN SATISFIED WITH
THE WAY THE JOB WENT DOWN.

419
00:28:52,464 --> 00:28:57,067
- NOT FOR 10 LARGE.
<i>- [ Electronic Ringing ]</i>

420
00:28:57,135 --> 00:29:00,336
- GET OVER THERE. MOVE!
-<i> YOU HAVE A VIDEO PHONE CALL.</i>

421
00:29:00,405 --> 00:29:02,939
<i> WHERE'S THE DAMN MONEY</i>
<i> YOU PROMISED US?</i>

422
00:29:03,008 --> 00:29:06,776
IT'S GOING TO BE MUCH HARDER
TO SELL NOW THAT IT'S BECOME
SUCH A SOUGHT AFTER COMMODITY.

423
00:29:06,845 --> 00:29:10,747
SOMEBODY'S GOING TO HAVE
TO PAY FOR THAT. THAT SOMEBODY
IS YOU PEOPLE.

424
00:29:10,816 --> 00:29:15,085
YOU'RE SCUM! YOU KNOW THAT?
I'M GONNA FIND YOU, PAL.
I WILL!

425
00:29:15,153 --> 00:29:18,321
EVEN IF YOU KNEW
WHERE I WAS, MR. JOB,
YOU'D NEVER HAVE THE NERVE.

426
00:29:18,390 --> 00:29:20,357
WELL, MAYBE NOT HIM, ELIJAH,

427
00:29:21,694 --> 00:29:25,195
BUT YOU FORGOT ABOUT ME.

428
00:29:28,533 --> 00:29:32,936
NOW, I'M GOING TO SEND
YOUR HEALTHY MESSENGER
BACK FOR OUR MONEY.

429
00:29:33,005 --> 00:29:37,708
IF HE ISN'T HERE IN TWO HOURS,
THE POLICE GET THE CANISTERS.
IS THAT CLEAR?

430
00:29:37,776 --> 00:29:41,478
CLEAR ENOUGH.
I JUST HOPE YOU ALL
LIVE LONG ENOUGH.

431
00:29:41,547 --> 00:29:45,114
OH, BY THE WAY,
THIS NOW ENDS
YOUR BROADCAST DAY.

432
00:29:47,519 --> 00:29:49,652
<i>[ Beeping ]</i>

433
00:29:56,795 --> 00:29:59,663
<i>WAIT A MINUTE. MIRAGE.</i>

434
00:30:02,367 --> 00:30:04,467
<i>THE E-MAIL WAS</i>
<i>FROM EDNA RAINES.</i>

435
00:30:05,870 --> 00:30:09,805
THAT'S IMPOSSIBLE.
SHE CAN BARELY SPEAK.

436
00:30:09,874 --> 00:30:12,542
IT SEEMS SHE'S HAD ANOTHER
MOMENT OF CLARITY.

437
00:30:12,610 --> 00:30:14,944
THAT'S NOT ALL.
IT'S MR. RAINES WHO STOLE IT.

438
00:30:15,013 --> 00:30:17,313
HOW WOULD MR. RAINES KNOW
WHAT WAS IN MY E-MAIL?

439
00:30:17,382 --> 00:30:21,684
LOOKS LIKE THEY'VE BEEN
MONITORING YOUR M-MAILBOX SINCE
LAST TUESDAY, MISS PARKER.

440
00:30:21,753 --> 00:30:25,755
<i>TUESDAY?</i>
<i>THAT'S THE VERY DAY EDNA</i>
<i>ESCAPED FROM THE INSTITUTION.</i>

441
00:30:25,824 --> 00:30:30,026
<i>HE MUST HAVE ANTICIPATED HER</i>
<i>CONTACTING YOU.</i>
WHAT WAS IN THE E-MAIL?

442
00:30:30,095 --> 00:30:33,829
WELL, THE TEXT FIELD WAS EMPTY.
BUT THERE WAS A VIDEO FILE
ATTACHED.

443
00:30:33,898 --> 00:30:35,665
- [ Typing ]
- PLAY IT.

444
00:30:35,734 --> 00:30:38,635
[ Beeps ]
UH-UH.

445
00:30:38,704 --> 00:30:42,838
THE ONLY WAY TO ACCESS
THE ACTUAL FILE IS FROM THE
COMPUTER IT WAS TRANSFERRED TO.

446
00:30:42,907 --> 00:30:46,309
<i>MR. RAINES'S OFFICE.</i>

447
00:30:46,378 --> 00:30:49,178
THEN WHAT ARE WE WAITING FOR?

448
00:30:49,248 --> 00:30:52,649
<i>I'M BLEEDING TO DEATH.</i>

449
00:30:52,718 --> 00:30:55,618
<i> LIKE ANY OF YOU CARE.</i>
<i> [ Coughing ]</i>

450
00:30:59,725 --> 00:31:01,958
SHOULDN'T HAVE
KILLED THAT LITTLE GIRL.

451
00:31:02,027 --> 00:31:04,728
THAT'S WHAT MADE
ELIJAH SO ANGRY.

452
00:31:04,796 --> 00:31:07,864
<i>NOW THERE'S THE GUARD.</i>

453
00:31:07,932 --> 00:31:10,233
WHICH ONE OF YOU DIRTBAGS
IS INTO SUFFOCATION, HUH?

454
00:31:10,302 --> 00:31:12,202
<i> WAS IT YOU?</i>

455
00:31:15,106 --> 00:31:18,041
[ Groans ]
WHAT HAPPENED THAT NIGHT?

456
00:31:18,110 --> 00:31:23,713
-<i> [ Coughing ]</i>
-<i> [ Siren Wails In Distance ]</i>

457
00:31:23,782 --> 00:31:26,649
<i> OH, WHAT THE HELL.</i>
<i> YOU'RE GONNA</i>
<i> BLEED TO DEATH ANYWAY.</i>

458
00:31:31,756 --> 00:31:34,423
A HUGE ESTATE IN WESTBROOK.

459
00:31:34,493 --> 00:31:37,827
INSIDE WERE
INTELLIGENCE DOCUMENTS.

460
00:31:37,896 --> 00:31:39,830
[ Scoffs ]
WORTH A FORTUNE.

461
00:31:42,000 --> 00:31:44,767
ELIJAH HIRED US TO GET 'EM.

462
00:31:44,836 --> 00:31:49,172
<i>WHOEVER FOUND THEM WAS SUPPOSED</i>
<i>TO BRING THEM BACK TO THE VAN.</i>

463
00:31:49,240 --> 00:31:51,608
BUT SOMEBODY GOT GREEDY,

464
00:31:52,978 --> 00:31:55,879
DECIDED TO TAKE A LITTLE
SIDE TRIP INTO THE GUESTHOUSE.

465
00:32:23,708 --> 00:32:26,642
CARETAKER'S DAUGHTER
WASN'T SUPPOSED TO BE THERE.

466
00:32:27,779 --> 00:32:29,713
I THINK CAIN DID HER.

467
00:32:29,781 --> 00:32:32,716
SHUT UP!
ALL FOR A FEW EXTRA BUCKS.

468
00:32:32,784 --> 00:32:34,717
[ Crunches ]
AAH!

469
00:32:34,786 --> 00:32:37,987
SHUT UP!
SHUT YOUR MOUTH!

470
00:32:39,624 --> 00:32:42,725
<i>[ Man Coughing ]</i>

471
00:32:45,297 --> 00:32:47,731
<i>MARK?</i>

472
00:32:48,900 --> 00:32:51,801
MARK, IS THAT YOU? HEY.

473
00:32:52,970 --> 00:32:54,904
<i>LOOK.</i>

474
00:32:54,973 --> 00:32:58,842
I'M REALLY-- I'M REALLY
SORRY ABOUT YOUR B-BIKE.

475
00:33:03,748 --> 00:33:08,118
<i>♪♪ [ Piano ]</i>
[ Sniffing ]

476
00:33:08,186 --> 00:33:12,421
WHAT'S THAT SMELL? IT SMELLS--
IT SMELLS LIKE PERFUME.

477
00:33:15,260 --> 00:33:17,260
<i>CUT IT OUT, GREEN BEAN.</i>

478
00:33:17,328 --> 00:33:21,631
<i>I DON'T WANT TO HEAR</i>
<i>THAT SONG AGAIN.</i>
<i>[ Gun Cocks ]</i>

479
00:33:21,699 --> 00:33:26,869
GO AHEAD. PLAY IT AGAIN, SAM,
JUST ONE MORE STINKIN' TIME.

480
00:33:26,938 --> 00:33:28,871
I DARE YOU.

481
00:33:35,013 --> 00:33:38,014
[ Sniffs ]
WHAT IS THAT SMELL?

482
00:33:38,083 --> 00:33:39,882
<i>IS THAT THE ANTIDOTE?</i>

483
00:33:39,951 --> 00:33:42,385
<i>[ Jarod ]</i>
<i>NO. IT'S</i> CHAMPS DE NUIT.

484
00:33:45,457 --> 00:33:48,592
MY MOTHER WORE IT.
<i>[ Helicopters Whir In Distance ]</i>

485
00:33:49,894 --> 00:33:54,364
I COULD SMELL IT WHEN
SHE'D TUCK ME IN BED AT NIGHT.

486
00:33:58,203 --> 00:34:01,771
[ Scoffs ]
MAYBE THAT'S A LIE.

487
00:34:03,641 --> 00:34:09,145
<i>'CAUSE I CAN BARELY</i>
<i>REMEMBER EVEN</i>
<i>IF I HAD A MOTHER.</i>

488
00:34:09,214 --> 00:34:12,482
♪♪ [ Calm ]

489
00:34:12,551 --> 00:34:16,052
THE INGREDIENTS IN PERFUME,
THEY'RE KNOWN AS NOTES,
DID YOU KNOW THAT?

490
00:34:19,124 --> 00:34:22,826
THE PERFUMER,
HE ACTS AS COMPOSER.

491
00:34:24,763 --> 00:34:27,330
NOW, ME, I ALWAYS WENT
FOR THE HEART.

492
00:34:27,398 --> 00:34:30,400
SOME PEOPLE, THEY COULD
ONLY SMELL THE TOP NOTES.

493
00:34:30,468 --> 00:34:33,937
<i>I WENT DEEPER TO</i>
<i>SEARCH FOR THE SOUL.</i>

494
00:34:34,005 --> 00:34:37,373
♪♪ [ Faster ]

495
00:34:37,441 --> 00:34:39,442
PERFUME.

496
00:34:39,510 --> 00:34:44,447
SPARKLING CITRUS NOTES,
LIKE LEMON. DARK RESONANT NOTES,
LIKE BALSAM.

497
00:34:47,986 --> 00:34:52,788
<i>♪♪ [ Loud, Heavy ]</i>

498
00:34:54,025 --> 00:34:55,958
[ Crash ]
<i> ♪♪ [ Stops ]</i>

499
00:34:56,027 --> 00:35:00,797
THE MEDICAL REPORT JUST HANDED
TO ME STATES THAT THE MAGNA
TECHNOLOGIES, LIMITED...

500
00:35:00,865 --> 00:35:05,135
SECURITY GUARD HAS
DIED FROM INJURIES SUSTAINED
DURING THE ROBBERY.

501
00:35:06,337 --> 00:35:07,770
WELL, THAT WAS SMART.

502
00:35:07,839 --> 00:35:11,307
HE'S DEAD! DIDN'T YOU
HEAR THAT? HE'S DEAD!

503
00:35:19,117 --> 00:35:21,283
<i>[ Jarod ]</i>
<i>HE AIN'T THE ONLY ONE.</i>

504
00:35:23,822 --> 00:35:26,756
<i>[ Eve ]</i>
<i>GREAT. THAT'S ONE MORE</i>
<i>CORPSE ON OUR HANDS.</i>

505
00:35:26,824 --> 00:35:30,660
OH, MY GOD.
I'M BLEEDING. OH, MY GOD.

506
00:35:30,729 --> 00:35:33,830
YOU'VE GOTTA FINISH THE STUFF.
I'M GONNA DIE. YOU'VE GOTTA
FINISH THAT STUFF!

507
00:35:33,899 --> 00:35:36,666
I'M FINISHING IT NOW.
LET GO OF ME!

508
00:35:50,181 --> 00:35:53,516
<i>♪♪ [ Music Box ]</i>

509
00:35:59,323 --> 00:36:02,025
OH, NO.
OH, GOD, IT'S HER.

510
00:36:02,093 --> 00:36:04,026
IT'S HER. IT'S THE TATE KID.

511
00:36:04,095 --> 00:36:07,964
<i> SO WHAT? IT'S HER.</i>
<i> SO WHAT?</i>

512
00:36:08,033 --> 00:36:11,734
<i>- SHE'S DEAD! JUST LIKE</i>
<i>  WE'RE GONNA BE.</i>
- I DIDN'T KILL HER. ALL RIGHT?

513
00:36:11,803 --> 00:36:14,804
I DIDN'T SAY YOU DID!
IT'S NOT EVEN HER PICTURE.

514
00:36:14,873 --> 00:36:18,107
<i>I DIDN'T KILL HER.</i>

515
00:36:18,176 --> 00:36:21,177
OH, DAMN IT!

516
00:36:25,484 --> 00:36:28,718
NOW THERE'S ONLY
ENOUGH ANTIDOTE F--
FOR FOUR OF US.

517
00:36:32,590 --> 00:36:34,890
<i>[ Eve ]</i>
<i>SO WHAT DOES THAT MEAN?</i>

518
00:36:34,959 --> 00:36:38,027
<i>[ Jarod ]</i>
<i>I GUESS THAT MEANS THAT</i>
<i>ONE OF IS GOING TO DIE.</i>

519
00:36:39,931 --> 00:36:42,799
<i> THE QUESTION IS, WHO?</i>

520
00:36:44,068 --> 00:36:46,135
<i>[ Helicopter Whirs In Distance ]</i>

521
00:36:49,040 --> 00:36:51,974
<i>[ Eve ]</i>
<i>SO HOW DO WE DECIDE</i>
<i>WHO GETS THE ANTIDOTE?</i>

522
00:36:52,043 --> 00:36:54,344
<i>[ Jarod ]</i>
<i>WE'LL LEAVE OUT THE ONE</i>
<i>WHO KILLED BRITTANY TATE.</i>

523
00:36:54,413 --> 00:36:56,946
ONLY PROBLEM IS WE DON'T
KNOW WHO THE KILLER IS.

524
00:36:57,015 --> 00:36:59,415
- WELL, WE DO.
- WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

525
00:36:59,484 --> 00:37:02,651
PROCESS OF ELIMINATION. I MEAN,
IT COULDN'T HAVE BEEN ME
BECAUSE I WASN'T THERE, RIGHT?

526
00:37:02,720 --> 00:37:06,022
I DIDN'T KILL HER. I SWEAR.
I DIDN'T KILL HER.
I DIDN'T KILL HER.

527
00:37:06,090 --> 00:37:09,191
NO. I KNOW<i> YOU</i> DIDN'T.

528
00:37:13,598 --> 00:37:15,865
AND I KNOW YOU DIDN'T.

529
00:37:18,770 --> 00:37:21,437
AND I KNOW...

530
00:37:24,208 --> 00:37:26,543
YOU DIDN'T.

531
00:37:26,611 --> 00:37:31,013
[ Gasps ]
WHAT'S GOING ON?
GIVE ME THE ANTIDOTE.

532
00:37:31,082 --> 00:37:34,950
- YOU DON'T DESERVE IT.
- WHAT? BUT WHY?

533
00:37:35,019 --> 00:37:40,155
BECAUSE...
YOU KILLED BRITTANY TATE.

534
00:37:44,729 --> 00:37:49,031
MR. ABRAHAM, I DON'T KNOW
WHAT YOU THINK YOU KNOW,
BUT YOU'RE WRONG.

535
00:37:49,100 --> 00:37:53,002
<i>AM I? FOR STARTERS, YOU'RE NOT</i>
<i>REALLY PREGNANT, ARE YOU?</i>

536
00:37:53,071 --> 00:37:57,240
THAT WAS JUST A FABRICATION SO
NO ONE WOULD BELIEVE YOU COULD
EVER POSSIBLY MURDER A CHILD.

537
00:37:57,308 --> 00:38:01,076
<i>AND I CHECKED YOUR BLOOD FOR</i>
<i>THE PREGNANCY HORMONE, H.C.G.</i>
<i>[ Imitates Buzzer ]</i>

538
00:38:01,145 --> 00:38:05,347
- THANKS FOR PLAYIN'.
- THE GAS IS MAKING YOU CRAZY.

539
00:38:05,416 --> 00:38:07,650
THE MOST CONVINCING
EVIDENCE WAS BRITTANY HERSELF.

540
00:38:07,719 --> 00:38:09,685
NO ONE SAW HER THAT NIGHT
EXCEPT FOR THE KILLER.

541
00:38:09,754 --> 00:38:11,854
HER PICTURE WASN'T IN THE
PAPERS. IT WASN'T ON THE NEWS.

542
00:38:11,922 --> 00:38:15,258
YOU WERE THE ONLY ONE
WHO RECOGNIZED THAT PHOTOGRAPH
AS A FAKE.

543
00:38:15,326 --> 00:38:18,661
<i>BECAUSE YOU REMEMBER</i>
<i>WHAT SHE LOOKED LIKE</i>
<i>THE NIGHT YOU KILLED HER.</i>

544
00:38:18,730 --> 00:38:22,398
-<i> [ Job ] WHOA! HEY.</i>
- PUT YOUR GUN DOWN.
PUT YOUR GUN DOWN.

545
00:38:22,467 --> 00:38:26,969
LOOK, IF SHE KILLED THE KID,
THEN SHE'S THE TICKET TO
OUR MONEY FROM ELIJAH.

546
00:38:27,038 --> 00:38:29,872
YOU SHOOT ME,
I TAKE AT LEAST
TWO OF YOU WITH ME.

547
00:38:29,941 --> 00:38:32,942
STARTING WITH LITTLE BROTHER.

548
00:38:33,010 --> 00:38:35,678
[ Groans ]

549
00:38:35,747 --> 00:38:40,450
<i>UH-OH, BLOODY NOSE.</i>
<i>YOU KNOW WHAT THAT MEANS.</i>

550
00:38:41,720 --> 00:38:44,620
YOU TELL ME THE TRUTH,
I'LL GIVE YOU HALF MY DOSE.

551
00:38:44,689 --> 00:38:48,090
[ Gasping ]
<i>DISINTEGRATION</i>
<i>OF YOUR INTERNAL ORGANS.</i>

552
00:38:48,159 --> 00:38:51,927
THE COMPLETE MELTDOWN OF
YOUR PSYCHE. IT ISN'T PRETTY.

553
00:38:56,601 --> 00:38:59,335
[ Sobs ]

554
00:38:59,404 --> 00:39:02,105
THE LITTLE GIRL
WASN'T SUPPOSED TO BE THERE.
<i>[ Jarod ] BUT SHE WAS THERE!</i>

555
00:39:02,173 --> 00:39:05,041
AND YOU KILLED HER IN COLD BLOOD
JUST TO ASSURE HER SILENCE!

556
00:39:05,109 --> 00:39:07,576
[ Gasping ]
OH, I CAN'T BREATHE!

557
00:39:07,645 --> 00:39:10,379
IT DOESN'T HAVE TO BE THIS WAY.
TELL ME THE TRUTH,
AND I'LL GIVE THIS TO YOU.

558
00:39:16,354 --> 00:39:20,089
YES, I KILLED HER!
I KILLED HER!
NOW GIVE IT TO ME!

559
00:39:24,528 --> 00:39:26,829
- OOPS.
- [ Screams ]

560
00:39:31,502 --> 00:39:35,104
[ All Panting ]

561
00:39:37,975 --> 00:39:40,543
BLANKS.

562
00:39:40,612 --> 00:39:42,912
YES. UH, EXCEPT FOR MINE.

563
00:39:42,980 --> 00:39:45,180
<i>[ Gunshots ]</i>

564
00:39:45,249 --> 00:39:47,784
OH, AND HIS.

565
00:39:51,323 --> 00:39:53,255
I THOUGHT YOU'D NEVER END THIS.

566
00:39:54,592 --> 00:39:56,859
I ALMOST SNEEZED.

567
00:39:56,928 --> 00:39:59,328
[ Wheezing ]
W-WHAT THE HELL'S GOING ON?

568
00:39:59,397 --> 00:40:01,263
I'M NOT EXACTLY
WHO I PRETEND TO BE.

569
00:40:01,332 --> 00:40:04,166
<i>I'M AN AGENT WITH THE TEXAS</i>
<i>BUREAU OF INVESTIGATION.</i>

570
00:40:04,235 --> 00:40:07,270
<i>I PURPOSELY EXPOSED YOU ALL</i>
<i>TO FIND OUT WHO KILLED</i>
<i>BRITTANY TATE.</i>

571
00:40:07,339 --> 00:40:09,138
BUT YOU WERE GONNA GET KILLED
BY THE GAS TOO.

572
00:40:09,207 --> 00:40:13,109
THERE WAS NO SOMAN GAS.
IT WAS JUST A 12 HOUR
INTESTINAL VIRUS...

573
00:40:13,178 --> 00:40:16,045
WITH A LITTLE KICKER TO
WEAKEN THE SINUS CAVITY
AND CONSTRICT BREATHING.

574
00:40:16,113 --> 00:40:19,182
<i>NOT TO MENTION A MILD</i>
<i>HERBAL HALLUCINOGEN.</i>

575
00:40:20,251 --> 00:40:23,051
IT'S COMPLETELY HARMLESS.

576
00:40:23,120 --> 00:40:27,490
<i>[ Creaking ]</i>

577
00:40:31,629 --> 00:40:34,730
<i>[ Radio Chatter ]</i>

578
00:40:42,874 --> 00:40:46,709
<i>[ Eve ]</i>
<i>I-I DON'T UNDERSTAND.</i>
<i>THE REPORTER, THE COPS?</i>

579
00:40:46,778 --> 00:40:48,711
IT WAS ALL A HOAX.

580
00:40:50,448 --> 00:40:52,648
MR. ELIJAH CUT A LITTLE DEAL
TO HELP US.

581
00:40:52,717 --> 00:40:54,684
<i>AND TO SHORTEN</i>
<i>HIS STAY IN PRISON.</i>

582
00:40:59,957 --> 00:41:05,895
NOW YOU SEE THEM.
NOW YOU DON'T.

583
00:41:05,964 --> 00:41:11,167
<i>THESE WERE ALL THE LAST THINGS</i>
<i>THAT BRITTANY SAW</i>
<i>BEFORE YOU KILLED HER.</i>

584
00:41:11,235 --> 00:41:13,502
<i> [ Lid Slams ]</i>

585
00:41:13,571 --> 00:41:15,505
NONE OF THIS WAS REAL?

586
00:41:15,573 --> 00:41:20,109
NOTHING.
EXCEPT YOUR CONFESSION.

587
00:41:20,178 --> 00:41:22,244
AND THAT'S
A LIFETIME OF REAL.

588
00:41:25,249 --> 00:41:27,583
<i>[ Radio Chatter ]</i>

589
00:41:27,652 --> 00:41:30,052
<i>[ Broots ]</i>
<i>I'M INTO RAINES'S HARD DRIVE.</i>

590
00:41:30,121 --> 00:41:32,054
THERE'S THE E-MAIL.

591
00:41:32,123 --> 00:41:34,690
BUT THE VIDEO ATTACHMENT'S
BEEN DELETED.

592
00:41:34,759 --> 00:41:36,726
- DAMN IT.
- HANG ON.

593
00:41:36,795 --> 00:41:38,894
DELETING E-MAILS
IS SORT OF LIKE
LOSING YOUR CAR KEYS.

594
00:41:38,963 --> 00:41:40,596
<i>THEY'RE NOT GONE, JUST LOST.</i>

595
00:41:40,665 --> 00:41:43,999
<i>FAINT MAGNETIC TRACES OF</i>
<i>THE ORIGINAL CAN STILL</i>
<i>LINGER WHERE THEY WERE STORED.</i>

596
00:41:44,068 --> 00:41:46,736
I JUST HAVE TO LINK
ALL THE PIECES.

597
00:41:51,976 --> 00:41:54,043
THERE. I GOT IT.

598
00:41:55,346 --> 00:41:58,314
<i>IT'S EDNA RAINES. SHE SURE</i>
<i>DOESN'T LOOK CRAZY THERE.</i>

599
00:41:58,382 --> 00:42:00,916
<i> MAYBE SHE'S NOT.</i>
<i> PLAY IT, QUICKLY.</i>

600
00:42:02,519 --> 00:42:04,653
MISS PARKER,
I NEED TO TALK TO YOU.

601
00:42:04,722 --> 00:42:07,823
IT'S TIME THAT YOU LEARNED
EVERYTHING ABOUT YOUR MOTHER
AND MIRAGE.

602
00:42:07,892 --> 00:42:12,728
<i>PLEASE ANSWER THIS MESSAGE</i>
<i>AS SOON AS POSSIBLE, AND I'LL</i>
<i>SEND YOU THE WHERE AND WHEN.</i>

603
00:42:12,797 --> 00:42:15,631
IT COULD BE A MATTER
OF LIFE AND DEATH.

604
00:42:15,699 --> 00:42:19,268
[ Sighs ]
FOR LEONARD, IT ALREADY IS.

605
00:42:19,337 --> 00:42:22,238
LET'S JUST HOPE IT'S NOT TOO
LATE FOR THE REST OF US.

606
00:42:26,210 --> 00:42:30,646
<i> IF ANYONE FINDS OUT</i>
<i> HOW WE PULLED THIS OFF,</i>
<i> SOME HEADS ARE GONNA ROLL.</i>

607
00:42:30,714 --> 00:42:33,950
- STARTING WITH MINE.
- WE CAUGHT A BABY KILLER,
DIDN'T WE?

608
00:42:35,320 --> 00:42:37,252
<i>[ Radio Chatter ]</i>

609
00:42:41,893 --> 00:42:44,861
RIGHT.
I'LL SEE YOU
BACK AT THE OFFICE.

610
00:42:44,929 --> 00:42:47,863
COME BOOK THESE ANIMALS.
UH, DON'T WAIT FOR ME.

611
00:42:47,932 --> 00:42:51,333
- YOU HAVE OTHER BUSINESS?
- FAMILY BUSINESS.

612
00:42:53,070 --> 00:42:55,004
[ No Audible Dialogue ]

613
00:42:57,041 --> 00:42:59,475
<i>[ Engine Starts ]</i>

614
00:43:04,716 --> 00:43:08,717
♪♪ [ Plays ]

615
00:43:08,786 --> 00:43:12,921
♪♪ [ Continues ]

616
00:43:16,994 --> 00:43:21,798
<i>♪♪ [ Piano ]</i>

